This is a wonderful NN hotel which provides great value for the price.	It is not in a tourist area and so we got a better price and a nicer room for our money.	U232 is a great little boutique hotel with excellent service and the quality of furnishings and detail is extremely good for the price.	There are good cafes nearby for lunch and breakfast & I don't think breakfast is of good value in U232 (14 euros per person).	Very reasonably priced and a great local atmosphere may it a highlite for us as an eatery.	This hotel is less expensive than most since its in a quiter part of the city.